"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-olympic-breakdancer-raygun-shuts-down-critics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.8252483183069861, \"rank\": 0.2117279030492783, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbOlympic breakdancer Raygun shuts down critics  Australian Olympic breakdancer Raygun, sparked a social media frenzy during the 2024 Paris Olympics with her creative dance style.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.8252483183069861, \"rank\": 0.2117279030492783, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 251, \"end\": 261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9996164662272794, \"rank\": 0.00038313586909609077, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 282, \"end\": 288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0957045121408419e-31, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian Olympic breakdancer Raygun, who sparked a whirlwind of social media debate during the 2024 Paris Olympics, has hit back at critics with a firm message: she's not here to conform.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 383, \"end\": 393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9996164662272794, \"rank\": 0.00038313586909609077, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0957045121408419e-31, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old, whose real name is Rachael Gunn, took theOlympicstage by storm.\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 610, \"end\": 617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9037231907482916e-16, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 618, \"end\": 622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.6208123928876335, \"rank\": 0.610790380507993, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not just with her moves, but with her unapologetic style and fierce commitment to originality, according toPeople.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the debut of breaking as an Olympic event, Raygun's unconventional dance style became the talk of the internet.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0957045121408419e-31, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Aussie breaker faced off against some of the world's top B-girls, including Team USA's Logistx and France's Syssy.\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 1006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 968, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999374022102, \"rank\": 3.144585750961901e-08, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 991, \"end\": 997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9810630456289974, \"rank\": 0.019270677576128274, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She did not walk away with victories in her round-robin battles.\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, she did walk away with her creative spirit intact.\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to ESPN after her performance, Raygun made it clear that she is not here to play by the traditional rules.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1146, \"end\": 1150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.108397093536799e-12, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}, {\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0957045121408419e-31, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was never going to beat these girls on what they do best - their power moves,\\\" Raygun said.\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1333, \"end\": 1339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0957045121408419e-31, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She acknowledged the strengths of her competitors.\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What I bring is creativity.\\\"\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her distinctive moves, which some online jokers dubbed \\\"kangaroo-like,\\\" did not win her the battles, but they certainly won her attention.\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Social media users were quick to compare her Olympic breakdancing style to that of an energetic child showing off their latest tricks.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Raygun is not fazed by the jabs, according toDaily Mail.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1709, \"end\": 1715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0957045121408419e-31, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All of my moves are original,\\\" she stated confidently.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Creativity is really important to me.\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I go out there, and I show my artistry.\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes it speaks to the judges, and sometimes it does not.\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do my thing, and it represents art.\\\"\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Raygun's performance sparked a larger conversation about the nature of Olympic breakdancing and the place of creativity in competition.\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2004, \"end\": 2010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0957045121408419e-31, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While some were quick to dismiss her Olympic breakdance style as too offbeat for the Olympic stage, others praised her for bringing something new and unique to the floor.\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's chef de mission, Anna Meares, also came to Raygun's defence.\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2313, \"end\": 2322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.7932756908862635, \"rank\": 0.26045388560796323, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2342, \"end\": 2353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Meares\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\"}, {\"begin\": 2368, \"end\": 2374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0957045121408419e-31, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She addressed the harsher side of the online commentary.\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meares, a former Olympic cyclist, did not hold back in calling out what she saw as sexist undertones in the criticism.\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love Rachael, and I think that what has occurred on social media with trolls and keyboard warriors, and taking those comments and giving them airtime, has been really disappointing,\\\" Meares said.\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2762, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2572, \"end\": 2579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9037231907482916e-16, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This  echoed the sentiment of many who felt that Raygun was unfairly targeted, accoridng toThe Guardian.\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2813, \"end\": 2819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0957045121408419e-31, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Olympic breakdancer Raygun is an absolutely loved member of this Olympic team,\\\" Meares continued.\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2891, \"end\": 2897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0957045121408419e-31, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She has represented the Olympic spirit with great enthusiasm.\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 3032, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I absolutely love her courage.\", \"from\": 3034, \"to\": 3068, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love her character, and I feel very disappointed for her, that she has come under the attack that she has.\\\"\", \"from\": 3069, \"to\": 3178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Raygun's journey to the Olympics wasn't an easy one.\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3180, \"end\": 3186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0957045121408419e-31, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A university lecturer in Sydney by day, she has spent years carving out her place in the male-dominated world of breaking.\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3259, \"end\": 3265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999999809379008, \"rank\": 1.9006593049486165e-08, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In 2008, she was locked in a room crying, being involved in a male-dominated sport as the only woman,\\\" Meares revealed.\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3478, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It took great courage for her to continue on and fight for her opportunity to participate in the Olympic breakdancing sport that she loved.\\\"\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the online noise, Raygun remains steadfast in her belief that Olympic breakdancing is about more than just power moves.\", \"from\": 3623, \"to\": 3750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3649, \"end\": 3655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0957045121408419e-31, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about creativity, originality, and, most importantly, self-expression.\", \"from\": 3752, \"to\": 3827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am all about creativity,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's something no amount of social media trolling can take away from her.\", \"from\": 3868, \"to\": 3947, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know by clicking on the comment tab below this article or by emailinginfo@thesouthafrican.comor sending a WhatsApp to 060 011 021 1.\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 4088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4062, \"end\": 4070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9999771574733646, \"rank\": 2.2843048328409723e-05, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can also follow@TheSAnews on XandThe South African on Facebookfor the latest news.\", \"from\": 4090, \"to\": 4176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 4178, \"to\": 4257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4178, \"end\": 4181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999994186143211, \"rank\": 5.762693321926366e-07, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 4182, \"end\": 4184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"score\": 0.999999990863671, \"rank\": 5.387497661958778e-09, \"text\": \"R2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writing positions available  Follow The South African on Facebook for the latest local and international news  Follow The South African's WhatsApp channel for the latest sport, lifestyle and local news  Follow The South African on X for the latest, breaking news  A brand new shopping mall is coming to Pretoria East, bringing major retailers and new convenience to the area.\", \"from\": 4258, \"to\": 4643, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4406, \"end\": 4414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9999771574733646, \"rank\": 2.2843048328409723e-05, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Orlando Pirates are reportedly set to welcome a new staff member in former Stellenbosch FC Head of Recruitment Brendon Fourie.\", \"from\": 4645, \"to\": 4771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4653, \"end\": 4660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piracy\", \"score\": 0.9999997263976558, \"rank\": 2.736024024780222e-07, \"text\": \"Pirates\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piracy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piracy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Masindi Nemtajela was stretched off during Orlando Pirates' 6-0 win over TS Galaxy on Sunday afternoon in Mbombela.\", \"from\": 4773, \"to\": 4888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4773, \"end\": 4780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masindi\", \"score\": 0.9884043144710486, \"rank\": 0.01173172289838061, \"text\": \"Masindi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masindi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Masindi\"}, {\"begin\": 4846, \"end\": 4855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TS_Galaxy_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TS Galaxy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TS_Galaxy_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TS_Galaxy_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 4879, \"end\": 4887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mbombela\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2872667650156555e-18, \"text\": \"Mbombela\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mbombela\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mbombela\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"IT support is not just technical, it is personal.\", \"from\": 4890, \"to\": 4939, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Liema Pantsi's victory was clouded as fans of the 'Big Brother Mzansi' show expressed that Smash Afrika was unprofessional towards her.\", \"from\": 4941, \"to\": 5076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4992, \"end\": 5003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Brother_(franchise)\", \"score\": 0.7225482040436585, \"rank\": 0.24191882124771444, \"text\": \"Big Brother\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Brother_(franchise)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Brother_(franchise)\"}, {\"begin\": 5038, \"end\": 5044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maghreb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.252882414448499e-17, \"text\": \"Afrika\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maghreb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maghreb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A dominant weekend for the SA teams in the URC has made a big impact on the latest log standings as the playoffs edge closer.\", \"from\": 5078, \"to\": 5203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5105, \"end\": 5107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.013542907065671e-15, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 5121, \"end\": 5124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\", \"score\": 0.9999767553322687, \"rank\": 1.8669808081422303e-05, \"text\": \"URC\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q10962\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheSouthAfrican.com is all about South Africa and the stories that affect South Africans, wherever they are in the world.\", \"from\": 5207, \"to\": 5328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5240, \"end\": 5252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999827196, \"rank\": 1.712463471958453e-11, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are independent.No agenda.No bias.\", \"from\": 5330, \"to\": 5367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our offices are for administrative purposes only, no visitors will be accepted without an appointment.\", \"from\": 5369, \"to\": 5471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa- Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd - Registration Number: 2005/028472/07 - Address: Regus Business Centre, 1st Floor, Block B, North Park, Black River Park, 2 Fir Street, Observatory, Cape Town, 7925, South Africa  Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 5473, \"to\": 5762, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5611, \"end\": 5621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_Great_Park\", \"score\": 0.999997195491982, \"rank\": 2.804515914086638e-06, \"text\": \"North Park\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_Great_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_Great_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 5655, \"end\": 5677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Observatory,_Cape_Town\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Observatory, Cape Town\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Observatory,_Cape_Town\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Observatory,_Cape_Town\"}, {\"begin\": 5685, \"end\": 5697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999827196, \"rank\": 1.712463471958453e-11, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc